%% Sequence — Download authorization (purchase gate + freemium quota)
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User / Guest
    participant C as Client (Download dialog)
    participant A as Server Action<br/>download authorization
    participant PS as PurchaseService
    participant QS as QuotaEnforcementService
    participant DB as Repositories
    participant S3 as AWS S3 / CloudFront

    U->>C: Click "Download" (format)
    C->>A: requestDownload(releaseId, formatType)
    A->>PS: getDownloadAccess(subject, releaseId)
    PS->>DB: findByUserAndRelease (purchase?)
    alt purchased
        PS-->>A: allow (paid)
    else free tier
        PS->>QS: check freemium quota (max 5 releases)
        QS->>DB: read UserDownloadQuota / GuestDownloadCount
        alt within quota
            QS-->>A: allow + reserve slot
        else quota exceeded
            QS-->>A: deny (QUOTA_EXCEEDED)
        end
    end
    alt allowed
        A->>S3: generate presigned GET (24h)
        S3-->>A: signed URL
        A->>DB: increment counter · log DownloadEvent
        A-->>C: signed URL
        C->>S3: download file
    else denied
        A-->>C: error (upgrade / limit message)
    end
